title: #194: Edge Of Wonder With Ben Chasteen and Rob Counts
description: Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome the host of the hit youtube channel Edge Of Wonder, Ben Chasteen and Rob Counts, to the show.  They take us through bizarre world of conspiracies.  This episode is off the hoot..  There are some technical difficulties towards the end but the show is off the hook!  Thank you for your support! Please check out youtube.com/edgeofwonder
